name: tired pixels #13
description:
Well..
You left the house for only five minutes. You even left the lights on. But over the years, something incredible and at the same time terrible has happened. Everything passed like a moment before my eyes. You tried to solve all problems with your brain alone. And finally, your home. Quietly entering inside you do not turn on the light and sit on an old armchair. You share this moment in an empty house with eternity and silence, which you are now afraid to destroy even with a switch. The old moon on the floor catches your tear.
